sat %>%
  mutate(pm10bad=ifelse(pm10>80,1,0),pm25bad=ifelse(pm25>35,1,0)) %>%
  mutate(pmbad=(pm10bad+pm25bad)) %>% 
  mutate(pmbad2=ifelse(pmbad!=1,pmbad,ifelse(pm10bad==1, 1, 1.5))) %>%
  group_by(pmbad2) %>% 
  summarise(count=n())
